result.name: transport-statistics-greater-manchester-road-traffic-section
result.notes:
This report presents results of HFAS’s (Transport for Greater Manchester Highways Forecasting and Analytical Services formerly known as GMTU) road traffic monitoring.  It includes trends in countywide and nationwide traffic flows.
